task.summary: ray, timing tests, vispy scenes, napari window against v0051
Signal controller to mediate communication between GUI and processor (without accessing data)
removed jones calculation adjusted ReconOrder state call to reflect property/getter/setter changes adjusted pyqtSlot window report
file pathing adjustments to work better with relative paths.
napari repo structure changed, adjusted to be non-breaking added signals for SignalController simplified init data added compute average implementation
vector calculation now adjusts length and rotates the vector about the midpoint of the pixel
default kernel is now passed as tuple.
added signal for length updates added observer to napari-gui length element updates
